&lt;p id="ysCq69"&gt;Google &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/3/23709318/google-accounts-passkey-support-password-2fa-fido-security-phishing"&gt;changed the feature in 2023&lt;/a&gt; to allow users to sign in with just a passkey — a...&lt;/p&gt;
